title: Cockroach Eggs
subtitle: The cause of swelling in a girl's jaw is determined to be cockroach eggs she ingested from eating a Taco Bell taco or licking envelopes. Real medical case or hoax?
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The cause of swelling in a girl’s jaw was determined to be cockroach eggs she ingested from eating a Taco Bell taco or licking envelopes.
